  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/3e1728cb2555b4199ef2115cc52adc27.webp?t=1759569193\" width=654 height=59 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The B.L.O.O.M (Biotech Lethal Offensive Organic Munitions) Initiative</i> is a fast-paced <strong>2D top-down shoot 'em up</strong> where you pilot a drone through procedurally generated battlefields. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=38 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/793c0967a60c59a6eca757b60b1fb91f.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=43 height=43 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/793c0967a60c59a6eca757b60b1fb91f.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=38 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/793c0967a60c59a6eca757b60b1fb91f.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=43 height=43 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/793c0967a60c59a6eca757b60b1fb91f.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=38 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/ddaed2eb127d3329fd1931d88abc4a5a.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Design your own levels </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build, test, and play your own levels using the same editor we used for the campaign and survival modes. Orchestrate enemy waves and boss encounters with precise timing, script on-screen briefings and prompts, choose your biome, map size, and starting funds, and set objectives like survival, relic hunts, or kill targets. Drop in spawners, buildings, resources, and power-ups, toggle weather effects, and tweak difficulty and time-of-day—then jump straight into the game to playtest and iterate. When you’re happy, package it up and share it with the community via Steam Workshop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/8d63ec53ed0ed9171207f64a05d03340.avif?t=1759569193\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design weapons inside the game from thousands of combinations. Load existing builds, set a custom weapon for your loadout, or start fresh from built-in templates like Spiral, Laser, and Missile. Edit, rename, and manage your creations, delete what you don’t need, and jump straight back into play to test them with your custom levels - no external tools required. These too can be shared with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/8620c3fce4c4e5b6281cc42e493eda84.avif?t=1759569193\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras_big/8620c3fce4c4e5b6281cc42e493eda84.avif?t=1759569193 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Or just play the built in Campaign or Survival sets of levels..</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Harvest, Build & Defend</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission: <strong>gather resources, plant lethal bio-organisms, and defend your bases</strong> from relentless alien and native species on the hostile planet <strong>Shlee</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/67dbb8a85b4dd94346aa1760fc4abe9c.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=480 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/67dbb8a85b4dd94346aa1760fc4abe9c.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/67dbb8a85b4dd94346aa1760fc4abe9c.mp4?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>From Training to Total War</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start in a basic training drone as you <strong>learn to build, plant, and fight</strong>, then dive into intense battles as two aggressive alien factions take an interest in your expanding operations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/f34750fae5268449213d509823feeeb4.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=480 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/f34750fae5268449213d509823feeeb4.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/f34750fae5268449213d509823feeeb4.mp4?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade, Adapt, and Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your drone, adapt your strategies, and <strong>survive against overwhelming odds in this fusion of action and strategy</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/1bf5ea9c424444e133be01ed359b1446.poster.avif?t=1759569193\" width=480 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/1bf5ea9c424444e133be01ed359b1446.webm?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543740/extras/1bf5ea9c424444e133be01ed359b1446.mp4?t=1759569193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
